    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order, providing a dependable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear, such as small surface scratches and light seat creasing, the car remains very clean and presentable. It\u2019s a perfect choice for someone looking for a high-quality, pre-owned vehicle that is ready to hit the road without any immediate concerns.",
